description:
This week we are joined by rapper and reality film star Chinese Kitty to discuss sex appeal and more. We ask her about where she stands in her love life to getting her to open up about if size really matters to her and golden showers. She shares why she is not feeling Love & HipHop anymore and how their editing ruined a sentimental moment with her and her mom. The duo and Chinese Kitty share tips on how to ooze sex appeal OUT OF THE BEDROOM and more.
